//****************How to Play Page*************** How to Play! Goal: Beat the dealer by getting closer to 21 by adding up the pip number on the card without going over. Important Rules: All face cards count as 10 points and aces can either count as 11 or 1. Otherwise the number on the card is its point value.
Buttons Deal: Start a new round. Stand: Stop dealing cards to you. Hit: Deal another card. Double Down: Stop dealing cards and double your current bet. Split: When dealt doubles split each card into new bet and deal a new card to each bet to be played separately. Fold: Stop play and exit current round.
//****************Tips N Tricks Page*************** Tips N Tricks! Tip 1: Stand when your hand is 12 through 16 and the dealer has a 2 through 6. Tip 2: Hit when your hand is 12 through 16 and the dealer has 7 through Ace. Tip 3: Always split Aces and 8s. Tip 4: Double down when you have 11 and the dealer has 2 through 10. Tip 5: Hit if the dealer has Aces through 6.
